INSTALL :
% perl Makefile.PL
% make
% make test
% make install


ABOUT :
A silly module to make perl act a bit more like Damien Conway ...

Well, he's done so much for the Perl community we might as well 
make him feel more at home <grin>


This was inspired by Ron Kimball's skit at the p5p impressions 
BOF at TPC5 in San Diego.


